---
import Layout from "../layouts/Default.astro";
import "../styles/main.css";
const title = "Sandra Rodgers";
const description = "Personal Website of Sandra Rodgers";
---

<Layout {title} {description}>
  <div class="projects">
    <img
      class="h-10 lg:h-16 relative -right-56 sm:-right-80"
      src="sparkles.webp"
    />
    <h1>Projects</h1>
    <h2 class="mt-20">Professional Projects</h2>
    <p>
      At <a href="deepgram.com">Deepgram</a>, I build and maintain the
      developers' website and the Deepgram blog with the DX team. I'm also
      currently building the new marketing site.
    </p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 xl:grid-cols-2 gap-10 sm:gap-4 mt-10">
      <a href="https://developers.deepgram.com/" class="hover:bg-black">
        <img class="rounded-sm h-54 sm:h-80" src="deepgram_devs.png" />
      </a>
      <a href="https://blog.deepgram.com/" class="hover:bg-black">
        <img class="rounded-sm h-54 sm:h-80" src="deepgram_blog.png" />
      </a>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-10">
      At <a href="alkami.com">Alkami</a>, I worked with the UXdev team to build
      and maintain the company's UI component library, IrisVue.
    </p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 xl:grid-cols-2 gap-10 sm:gap-4 mt-10">
      <a href="https://iris-vue.alkami.design/" class="hover:bg-black">
        <img class="rounded-sm h-54 sm:h-80" src="iris_vue.png" />
      </a>
    </div>
    <h2 class="mt-20">Vue Mastery</h2>
    <p>
      Iâ€™m currently creating learning content for <a
        class="vue-mastery"
        href="https://vuemastery.com"
        target="_blank">Vue Mastery</a
      >
      about Vue's new official state managment library, <a
        href="https://pinia.vuejs.org/">Pinia</a
      >! My new Pinia Patterns course is coming out in March 2023!
    </p>
    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3 gap-10 sm:gap-4 mt-10"
    >
      <a href="https://www.vuemastery.com/courses" class="hover:bg-black">
        <img class="rounded-sm h-54 sm:h-80" src="pinia_patterns.png" />
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://www.vuemastery.com/courses/pinia-fundamentals/fundamentals-what-is-pinia/"
        class="hover:bg-black"
      >
        <img class="rounded-sm h-54 sm:h-80" src="pinia_fundamentals.png" />
      </a>
    </div>
  </div></Layout
>

<style scoped>
  .projects {
    @apply h-full;
    @apply px-10 sm:px-16 lg:px-44;
    @apply py-28 sm:py-32 lg:py-10;
  }

  h1 {
    @apply text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl !important;
  }

  .vue-mastery {
    @apply text-three hover:bg-three hover:text-black;
  }
</style>
